    "name": "ノナプルナイン：アシンプトート",
    "steam_appid": 3145650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/7f1a6353ef7b699157d18d4496d132df.poster.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/7f1a6353ef7b699157d18d4496d132df.webm?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/7f1a6353ef7b699157d18d4496d132df.mp4?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/66cb80db638edbf0d53a07862f28410b.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=75 /></span>The girl wakes up in a research facility, where the same 32nd floor loops….</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the test subject, “Nonuple Nine” to explore the building in side-view perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on points of interest, collect information and solve the mystery of this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/de32f0a73e2af2088c0f135a5a240cca.poster.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/de32f0a73e2af2088c0f135a5a240cca.webm?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/de32f0a73e2af2088c0f135a5a240cca.mp4?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/25bc0e7a6726b0646225a3edb4245b51.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=75 /></span>You can find manga, online meeting logs on computers, and business documentary programs on TVs, in different formats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Containing more than 1700 graphic files, events have their own visual styles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overwhelming density of the visual presentations will make you want to see more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything you see is there to progress the plot to the climax.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the latest scientific findings and the supervision from experts, this game will change how you “perceive the world”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/fdde46b8f0bd6000d86d2ded1ed3f992.poster.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/fdde46b8f0bd6000d86d2ded1ed3f992.webm?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/fdde46b8f0bd6000d86d2ded1ed3f992.mp4?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/b5a5f1c4ced112325be2abc6bb94e1bb.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=75 /></span>The developer of this game was the scenario writer for several titles in the “Ace Attorney” series.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The BGM for this game was created by the composer of “5 Centimeters per Second”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While being a small-scaled indie development, this roughly 30 hours game took more than a decade to create.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/ff3ac3812789e4f6e374ae43291ea3e6.poster.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/ff3ac3812789e4f6e374ae43291ea3e6.webm?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/ff3ac3812789e4f6e374ae43291ea3e6.mp4?t=1727927940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/b0f6f7a7864f37e33e07671b473a7b64.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q1: Is this a Horror game?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the game contains dead bodies and blood, but I do not intend the game to be scary, and I aim to provide surprise in discovering the truth and insights, which also come with suspense and curiosity. There will be no loud “jumpscares”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q2: Is this an Escape Rooms game?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escaping from the facility is your goal, but this is not a traditional “Escape Room game”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are little action or puzzle elements included, and the game focuses on exploration and story. You won’t need to have good skills or reflexes to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q3: Are these trailers and screenshots on the storepage part of cutscenes?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are very few “cutscenes” where you can only watch and cannot interact. Most of the events happen as you progress on your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/b0f6f7a7864f37e33e07671b473a7b64.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145650/extras/71dbe48d8b5a787b83d5eeb08432ae05.avif?t=1727927940\" width=616 height=1050 /></span></p>",
